snippet.title: 1st Kochobo Dourado Collab v3.0 - Hack of Super Mario World [SNES]
snippet.description:
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
¦ 1st KOCHOBO DOURADO COLLAB (v3.0) ¦
¦-------------------------------------------------------------¦
¦ A crazy collab made by Mario Hacks Team/TheMorganah ¦
2020~2023

https://www.smwcentral.net/?p=section&a=details&id=34370
Kochobo Dourado is a level design, overworld and kaizo contest
by Mario Hacks, the brazillian smwhacking community. 

Features:
- Play any level in the order that you wish.
- 14 entries made by amazing people.
- A colorful and happy overworld.
- High Quality Rips soundtrack.
- 3 bosses to fight.

v3.0 - [Ice Castle] More P-Speed moment.
     - Game is now 100% brazillian portuguese (PT-BR).
     - Minor tweaks (and surprises!).

#supermarioworld #romhack #snes
